This repository is derived from Arithmetic Tracker for Zetamac by Nathan Negera.

- Upstream add-on page: https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/arithmetic-tracker-for-zetamac/
- Upstream license: MIT License

Changes in this repository include:

- Google Apps Script webhook integration
- Google Sheets remote upload queueing
- Firefox transport workarounds for Apps Script redirects and preflight behavior
- Public deployment documentation and packaging helpers
- Extension identity changes to avoid conflicting with the upstream AMO add-on
